</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="9.[160,1155,141,236]" pageId="9" pageNumber="1920">
From the following sampling locations: 8C, 14A, 14C, 16B (see 
<tableCitation box="[878,961,178,202]" captionStart="Table 1" captionStartId="5.[158,214,499,522]" captionText="Table 1. Supralittoral sampling locations in Bermuda." pageId="9" pageNumber="1920">Table 1</tableCitation>
